1951;;The Prince Who Was a Thief;;American;;Rudolph Mate;;Tony Curtis, Piper Laurie;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Prince_Who_Was_a_Thief;;An assassin (Everett Sloane) is sent to kill a baby prince but cannot go through with it. He decides to raise the child as his own, and he grows up to be a thief (Tony Curtis).